    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[ITB 0.0.8]]></title>
        <id>https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8</id>
        <link href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8"/>
        <updated>2026-04-10T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[This release of ITB 0.0.8 focuses on practical workflow improvements, broader customization options, and measurable performance gains for data modeling.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This release of <strong>ITB 0.0.8</strong> focuses on practical workflow improvements, broader customization options, and measurable performance gains for data modeling.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-release-overview">📦 Release Overview<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#-release-overview" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 📦 Release Overview" title="Direct link to 📦 Release Overview" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>This release bundles significant improvements across components:</p>
<table><thead><tr><th>Component</th><th>Version</th><th>Focus</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>WebApp</strong></td><td>0.0.8</td><td>7 UI/UX features + Performance optimization</td></tr><tr><td><strong>API</strong></td><td>0.0.8</td><td>No changes (only alignment with WebApp)</td></tr></tbody></table>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-webapp-008">🎯 WebApp 0.0.8<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#-webapp-008" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🎯 WebApp 0.0.8" title="Direct link to 🎯 WebApp 0.0.8" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p><strong>7 UI/UX Features + Comprehensive Performance Optimization</strong></p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="highlights">Highlights<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#highlights" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Highlights" title="Direct link to Highlights" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<h4 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-advanced-workflows">🎯 Advanced Workflows<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#-advanced-workflows" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🎯 Advanced Workflows" title="Direct link to 🎯 Advanced Workflows" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li class="">✨ <strong>Drag Entity from Sidebar to Canvas</strong> - Intuitive drag-and-drop entity placement</li>
<li class="">✨ <strong>Drag &amp; Context Menu for Related Entities</strong> - Explore relationships without sidebar searching</li>
<li class="">✨ <strong>Comprehensive Canvas Context Menus</strong> - Right-click actions for entities, edges, and canvas</li>
<li class="">✨ <strong>User Settings Dialog</strong> - Centralized preferences for language, theme, canvas behavior, and grid</li>
<li class="">✨ <strong>Generate All Artifacts Button</strong> - One-click artifact generation with progress tracking</li>
<li class="">✨ <strong>Entity Tree Auto-Reveal</strong> - Canvas selection automatically reveals and scrolls to entity in sidebar</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-performance">⚡ Performance<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#-performance" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to ⚡ Performance" title="Direct link to ⚡ Performance" translate="no">​</a></h4>
<ul>
<li class="">⚡ <strong>Canvas Rendering Performance Boost</strong> - 60%+ render time reduction for large viewpoints<!-- -->
<ul>
<li class="">Viewport culling: Only visible elements rendered</li>
<li class="">Shared data maps for entity types and attributes</li>
<li class="">Lazy edge labels (hidden below 50% zoom)</li>
<li class="">Singleton dialogs: One instance for entire canvas</li>
<li class="">Cached handle positions for edge routing</li>
<li class="">Debounced viewpoint switching batched via requestAnimationFrame</li>
<li class=""><strong>Result:</strong> Large 30-entity, 40-edge viewpoints now render in under 10 seconds (vs. ~25 seconds)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>→ <a class="" href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog-webapp/webapp-0.0.8">View WebApp 0.0.8 Release Details</a></p>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-summary">🎓 Summary<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#-summary" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🎓 Summary" title="Direct link to 🎓 Summary" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>ITB 0.0.8 is a focused update that improves day-to-day modeling workflows and responsiveness. The 7 UI features reduce interaction overhead, and the 60%+ rendering improvement makes larger viewpoints easier to work with in regular usage.</p>
<p><strong>Key Achievements:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li class="">✅ Intuitive drag-and-drop workflows</li>
<li class="">✅ Context-aware actions reduce clicks</li>
<li class="">✅ Customizable workspace settings</li>
<li class="">✅ 60%+ performance improvement</li>
<li class="">✅ Large models now production-ready</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="️-upgrade-notes">⚠️ Upgrade Notes<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#%EF%B8%8F-upgrade-notes" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to ⚠️ Upgrade Notes" title="Direct link to ⚠️ Upgrade Notes" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>New Docker Compose File and new .env File! Please update.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="recommended-actions">Recommended Actions<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#recommended-actions" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Recommended Actions" title="Direct link to Recommended Actions" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ol>
<li class=""><strong>Backup your current workspace:</strong> Export any critical models before upgrading</li>
<li class=""><strong>Clear browser cache:</strong> Some CSS and layout changes may require cache refresh</li>
<li class=""><strong>Test large models:</strong> If working with models exceeding 50 entities, test the new performance improvements</li>
</ol>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="compatibility">Compatibility<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#compatibility" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Compatibility" title="Direct link to Compatibility" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">✅ Fully backward compatible with existing models</li>
<li class="">✅ Storage layout unchanged</li>
<li class="">✅ API format unchanged</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-thank-you">🙏 Thank You<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.8#-thank-you" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🙏 Thank You" title="Direct link to 🙏 Thank You" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Thank you to all contributors and users who shared feedback and tested pre-release versions. That input helped refine this release.</p>
<hr>
<p><em>ITB 0.0.8 — March 20, 2026</em></p>]]></content>
    </entry>
